{
 "name": "RPlog_Revolutions_End",
 "title": "Revolution's End",
 "summary": "A massive battle erupts over Nar Shaddaa and Nal Hutta as the Imperial flagship Predator, anchoring a fleet above the Smuggler's Moon, launches dozens of troop ships and fighters down into the atmosphere. The Sith Lord Darth Malign joins the assault personally, leading a black-painted squadron of TIE Interceptors in his X-wing, while New Republic and allied forces -- Luke Skywalker, the smuggler-admiral Axel, Keline, Odion, and Xar'on among them -- rally to oppose the invasion. The swirling space and ground engagement brings a revolution to its bloody close, the Empire and Sith pressing their crushing assault on the Hutt world.",
